    public class HwProcessorImpl
extends HwComputingResourceImpl
implements HwProcessor
    An implementation of the model object 'Hw Processor'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Architecture
    • Mips
    • Ipc
    • Nb Cores
    • Nb Pipelines
    • Nb Stages
    • Nb AL Us
    • Nb FP Us
    • Owned IS As
    • Predictors
    • Caches
    • Owned MM Us
